br />\n唔好日日FF每份工都九成人係黃絲啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b32b9ab59060d4258ab15f665322807159d0c2","tid":1498162,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>聽日824對家吹大雞發動萬人圍港台<br />\n中共又發動宣傳機器想港台跪同清洗</strong><br />\n<br />\n營救香港電台！對家堅吹大雞萬人圍 配合國家機器滅利君雅鏗鏘集頭條新聞聲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afeaiKU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afeaiKU</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一人一信撐港台<br />\n去信廣管局</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fba_archives.ofca.gov.hk%2Fcn%2Fcontact%2F&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=6dd2f677\" target=\"_blank\">https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依個唔算投訴，咪當意見咁send<br />\n記得話港台31,32台都有睇，做得好，最like咩節目同點解<br />\n唔好太黃絲feel 同唔好用standard form<br />\n會只當一份意見</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝瀏覽我們的網址。如有任何有關廣播事務的查詢，可按以下方式與我們聯絡： <br />\n<br />\n以電子郵件方式傳送至<br />\nba@tela.gov.hk<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3faRZNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3faRZNL.jpg&h=796e8d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以書面方式寄</strong><br />\n廣播事務管理局秘書處<br />\n經影視及娛樂事務管理處<br />\n香港灣仔告士打道5號<br />\n稅務大樓39樓<br />\n(傳真號碼：(852) 2507 2219)<br />\n<br />\n致電查詢電話號碼：(852) 2594 5721"},{"pid":"0626034d30d7719888d6dc001e630430ede7c38a","tid":1498162,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"仲要支持因航吖嘛，唔返工因航點賺錢，因航唔賺錢即係唔撐佢<br />\n<br />\n我地仲要繼續睇下因航點樣受支那民航處恐嚇"},{"pid":"47efe935331023511cd1304be1946b2158a77644","tid":1498162,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80c09448daf587df46721148a07eb4ec7fad30e5","tid":1498162,"uid":25284